<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="65 00 00 01 00 00 00 09">我決定，<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
等我長大之後，<delay20 />
要變成「超級英雄」喔～</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="101_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />遇到困難，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會來救你的喔～！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算我戴著變身用的面具，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要發現<delay8 />那個人就是我喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為超級英雄可以在天空中飛，<delay20 />
如果<delay8 />有人遇到麻煩，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就可以馬上去幫忙啦～<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />也可以<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />依靠我喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為超級英雄很強、<delay8 />很帥、<delay8 />很溫柔<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我覺得好厲害喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想就算是要把洋蔥切碎碎的，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超級英雄也一定不會哭的吧～<delay frames="40" />
感覺就很強～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="66 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實<delay8 />我從很久以前<delay20 />
就在偷偷收集某樣東西喔～</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="102_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欸嘿嘿，<delay20 />其實啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是「橡皮擦的屑屑」喔～<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然一點用都沒有，<delay20 />
但我會把屑屑一點一點放進瓶子裡，拿來欣賞喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />變成橡皮擦屑屑的我的字<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺很神祕吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欸嘿嘿，<delay20 />其實啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是「牛奶瓶的蓋子」喔～<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或許有一天<delay8 />
牛奶瓶的蓋子也能當鈴錢用喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣一來，<delay20 />
我也是有錢人了耶～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欸嘿嘿，<delay20 />其實啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是「果汁瓶的瓶蓋」喔～<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我現在還沒想到<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個可以用來做什麼～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="0a 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可以聽我說說嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<tag a="110" b="0" />
有一件煩惱的事～<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實晚上我不開電燈的話，<delay20 />
就會睡不好呀<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xb 0xc 0xd" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果在黑漆漆的房間裡，<delay20 />
有某個地方發出
奇怪的聲音<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇啊～！<delay frames="40" />
光是用想的就覺得好可怕，<delay20 />
這樣我不敢一個人去上廁所啦～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
我遇到危險的時候，<delay20 />
你要來救我喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果在黑漆漆的房間裡，<delay20 />
有鬼來搔我癢的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管是鬼<delay20 />
還是被搔癢，<delay20 />
我<delay8 />都超怕的啦～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我到底該害怕還是該大笑呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
你覺得應該要怎麼做比較好呢～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">如果在黑漆漆的房間裡，<delay20 />
那隻黑黑的蟲蟲<delay20 />
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />飛出來的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚哇～！<delay frames="40" />
光是用想的<delay20 />
就覺得背癢癢的～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我自己一個人會很害怕，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />，如果發生了什麼事，<delay20 />
你一定要來救我喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="60" b="0" arg="0xf 0x10" /></message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我跟你說喔，<delay20 />
我之前看到的雲朵啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />長得像是酥酥脆脆的牛角麵包耶～<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為看起來實在是太好吃了，<delay20 />
所以我就一直看著天空走路，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果不小心跌倒了～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是發現看起來很好吃的雲朵，<delay20 />
真的要小心點才行啊～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="7" arg="0x110f 0x1200 0xcd00" /></message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我長大之後<delay20 />
想要學會在天空飛翔～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是要馬上學會好像很困難，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<delay8 />我都在夢裡<delay8 />
努力練習飛翔喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在想我長大之後，<delay20 />
是不是有可能<delay20 />
學會在天上飛翔呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我覺得一定很困難，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以已經在夢裡面<delay20 />
拼命練習了～<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay20 />
也想練習的話，<delay20 />
還是早點開始會比較好喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="14 00 00 01 00 00 00 09">我最近啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超愛吃<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />的～</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x15 0x16 0x17" /></message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然直接吃也很好吃，<delay20 />
但如果用心做成一道料理的話，<delay20 />
會變得更好吃喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得是因為<delay20 />
做料理的人在裡頭加入了自己的心意，
所以才會變得更好吃喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道心意究竟是
什麼樣的味道呢～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是回想起<delay20 />
那酸酸甜甜的香味，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就覺得好幸福喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<delay8 />我的家裡有<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />樹的話，<delay20 />
不管是下雨天，或是在夢裡面，<delay20 />
都能享受它的香味耶～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果有一天<delay20 />
世界上的所有<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />都消失的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家會不會覺得<delay20 />
是因為我吃太多才變成那樣？<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是我只是<delay20 />
很喜歡很喜歡<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />而已啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="19 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有時會做些體操來活動身體喔～</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="025_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />彎曲膝蓋蹲下來<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
然後伸展身體站起來！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣做感覺能增強腿部呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但要是一個不注意，<delay20 />
有時候會不小心往後倒！<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />做起來還挺刺激的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />將身體往前倒下<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
然後張開雙手往後大大地伸展！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣就能伸展身體，<delay8 />感覺很舒服喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是，<delay8 />如果在吃飽後做，<delay20 />
往前倒時會壓到肚子，<delay8 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人感到有些不舒服呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有規律地<delay8 />交互抬起<delay20 />左右的大腿！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要這麼做，身體就會暖起來喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然這個動作<delay8 />看起來像是在跳舞，
做起來似乎很開心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但其實相當地累人喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="025_04" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />舉起一隻手，將身體向旁邊彎曲！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />腋下雖然會變得緊繃<delay8 />甚至有點痛，<delay20 />
但同時也很舒服喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我推薦<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在彎曲身體時，<delay8 />
用另一邊的手扶住腰部！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來是不是很帥啊～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="026" attrib="1b 00 00 01 00 00 00 09">你能聽聽我之前經歷的事情嗎～？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那件事情<delay8 />發生在
我看完恐怖電影後的當晚<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="027_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在睡夢中<delay8 />覺得不太對勁，<delay20 />
就突然醒來了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />醒來後感到全身一陣疼痛<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />隨後<delay8 />我便急忙起身<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果發現自己睡在地板上。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的睡相真的太差了～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="027_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />門發出像開關門<delay8 />又像呻吟的聲音<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之就是發出了怪聲，<delay20 />
所以我就醒來了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後<delay8 />我急忙起身查看，<delay20 />
結果那聲音已經消失了。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />難道那是我磨牙的聲音！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="027_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我聞到房間裡有種<delay8 />
東西腐爛後的怪味，<delay20 />
所以我就醒來了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後我急忙起身查看，<delay20 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />發現那是我不小心忘記丟廚餘，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />廚餘腐爛後發出的味道～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="028" attrib="1d 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我小時候很喜歡玩一個遊戲，<delay20 />
當時我常常和附近的朋友一起玩喔。<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我來告訴你那是什麼遊戲吧～</message>
	<message label="029" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="029_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那個遊戲<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是跳繩喔！<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過因為大家都想跳繩，<delay20 />
所以總是決定不了誰要去揮動繩子<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果<delay8 />最後只能把所有繩子接起來<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />玩扮演電車的遊戲。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />真令人懷念啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="029_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那個遊戲<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是扮家家酒喔！<10_4 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我記得當時都是用猜拳<delay20 />
來決定要扮演的角色～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後嬰兒是其中最受歡迎的角色喔～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為<delay8 />大家都會來照顧嬰兒，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嬰兒只要負責睡覺就行了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="029_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那個遊戲<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是藏鞋子喔！<10_4 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過當時年紀小，<delay20 />常常玩到後面
忘記自己把鞋子藏到哪去呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我到底<delay8 />弄丟了幾隻鞋子啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />不知道藏起來的鞋子，<delay20 />
是不是<delay8 />還在當時的地方，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>